{"tid":1794773,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"小白兔1個月大同而加5歲都好可愛搞gag !!!","createTime":"2019-12-23T11:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T16:07:29.000Z","uid":197098,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c2004444f1a59766fbb3a1156ac36c00b6422da","tid":1794773,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T11:13:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">1個月大，食紅甜椒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZxRYr1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZxRYr1.jpg&h=f18ab9fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TSqHkFo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTSqHkFo.jpg&h=8179a9cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">5歲大:</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2X4UbNf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2X4UbNf.jpg&h=878f0924&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>錄咗個影片:</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WGN1HtIEHxA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWGN1HtIEHxA&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=3de318ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WGN1HtIEHxA</a>"},{"pid":"9f345b9c7134cf6865ed2715787802bf397cc2a5","tid":1794773,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T12:04:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c70d406077aa7b6e6376567458e15abb1e00021","tid":1794773,"uid":249794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T12:06:06.000Z","msg":"兔兔!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358c31f9b15d28e6be8b41ac6bde56647e798b5f","tid":1794773,"uid":161190,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T12:12:03.000Z","msg":"好大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce26d06c94ddf29989dfa3c456a2adfded4fdd39","tid":1794773,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T13:26:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">兔子<strong><em><ins>側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西</ins></em></strong>。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面睇唔到)&nbsp;<strong><em><ins>你在牠後面也會看到你</ins></em></strong>。兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱, 另外也有遠視。所以牠們不是無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。</span>"},{"pid":"053b5e7f307cb072b6a51b4205fc8e3d1ac1a2c0","tid":1794773,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T15:30:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子是應該要被絕育</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 兔子是被捕獵動物(Prey animal), 是大自然內每個捕獵者(Predator)的目標, 狗吠聲、消防車叫聲、小孩尖叫、雷暴等也會嚇驚兔子, 所以不建議帶出外散步。兔子是全世界其中一個最多被棄養的動物(在美國排第3最多被棄養), 很多人將牠放生, 這樣會令兔子十分恐慌, 而且沒有覓食能力(寵物兔和野兔是不同), 有些人送給兔協, 但容納不到那麼龐大的數目。<br />\n<br />\n2. 絕育後會大大減少因荷爾蒙控制而霸地盤，不會隨地去廁所 (兔子是不需要訓練去廁所，只要廁所內有紙棉和乾草和夠大便可以, 建議用貓廁所)<br />\n<br />\n3. 荷爾蒙減少令攻擊性減少，更加溫馴和親人，也會活得更開心。如果想將2隻兔合養(做夫妻/好朋友)要先絕育才容易建立關係, 否則有機會打架！<br />\n<br />\n4. 兔子是很容易患上生殖器病動物，所以絕育會令到更健康和長壽！<br />\n<br />\n5. 減少過量繁殖(和棄養後所面對的困境)，繁殖得快和多。"},{"pid":"cc234f496bc4a1eb34dfce97f392ebf6e51a50d8","tid":1794773,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T03:34:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">Season's greetings! Wishing you a season full of Yuletide cheer!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8cd9f60fa923b35824bc97f73845773edd24f06","tid":1794773,"uid":194894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"358c31f9b15d28e6be8b41ac6bde56647e798b5f","tid":1794773,"uid":161190,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T12:12:03.000Z","msg":"好大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:09:42.000Z","msg":"但係個啲係兔毛定胸毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b53db7b57a7d7f4a34adb8bbab6c60f3a06ac1","tid":1794773,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8cd9f60fa923b35824bc97f73845773edd24f06","tid":1794773,"uid":194894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"358c31f9b15d28e6be8b41ac6bde56647e798b5f","tid":1794773,"uid":161190,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T12:12:03.000Z","msg":"好大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:09:42.000Z","msg":"但係個啲係兔毛定胸毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:58:19.000Z","msg":"chest"},{"pid":"bdaebbe74ee6ed18bcda0dd7b8f0b75dbc390067","tid":1794773,"uid":194894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f5b53db7b57a7d7f4a34adb8bbab6c60f3a06ac1","tid":1794773,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8cd9f60fa923b35824bc97f73845773edd24f06","tid":1794773,"uid":194894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"358c31f9b15d28e6be8b41ac6bde56647e798b5f","tid":1794773,"uid":161190,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T12:12:03.000Z","msg":"好大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T04:09:42.000Z","msg":"但係個啲係兔毛定胸毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" cl